{
  "texts": [
    "However, this method still provides limited insight into how condensed graphs represent the original data [119].",
    "An explainable condensation can illuminate the intricate patterns within the graph, thereby enhancing user trust and acceptance.",
    "This is particularly important in sectors like healthcare [120] and finance [36], where the interpretability and justification of decision-making processes are critical.",
    "Consequently, by elucidating the logic behind data transformations, explainable GC has the potential to open up new avenues for its application, establishing GC as a more reliable and transparent tool in data-centric technology fields.",
    "This survey presents an up-to-date and comprehensive overview of GC and classifies the existing research into five distinct categories aligned with the proposed essential GC evaluation criteria."
  ]
}